title: CSCT student wins Faraday Discussion poster prize (University of Bath)
text: ( Source : University of Bath ) George Gregory went to the Faraday Discussion - Carbon Dioxide Utilisation in Sheffield to present a poster and won the poster prize. Here is George 's account on her trip: A conference with a difference ! Held
